data.description: One of the original HISTORIC homes in Springtown, this beautifully updated 6 bedroom home is a rare find! You will not find another that has the charm and spacious living that this home has to offer!! Located on 3 acres just 1 block from Springtown Elementary and a short walk to the CITY PARK! Bring your large family and kids to play in the TWO-STORY playhouse that is a replica of this STUNNING home. Country living at its finest! This could be a great possibility for a BED AND BREAKFAST or WEDDING VENUE. Come and see!!
